New Orleans Pelicans beat the San Antonio Spurs 108-103 to reach the NBA play-offs . 
  Anthony Davis had 31 points and 13 rebounds as the Pelicans earned their first play-off berth since 2011 . 
  Memphis Grizzlies beat the Indiana Pacers 95-83 to secure the No 8 seed in the Eastern Conference . 
  Oklahoma City Thunder beat Minnesota Timberwolves 138-113 to make the playoffs . 
  Brooklyn Nets beat the Orlando Magic 101-88 to qualify for the post-season . 
  Golden State Warriors beat the Denver Nuggets 133-126 . 
  Marc Gasol scored 33 points for the Grizzlies . 
 